<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_347" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_347_r1l1">Eraſmen von wıſentaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_347_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eraſem als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . wıe eẅch ʒwen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> arm - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l3"><expan>man<ex>n</ex></expan> fürbracht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Jn ſey geſagt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ ſıe vor vns <expan>vnſıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l4">ſein <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> wır dar = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l5">cʒu niht wol <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / als Jrſelbs wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mugt / Vns <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l6">denn dıe <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> leẅt dıe dıe ſache berürt mıt <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l7">Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_347_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Leonhardȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_347" id="172v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erasmen von Wisentaw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Erasem, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch
                                                zwen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> fürbracht
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, in sey gesagt
                                                  <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz sie vor uns
                                                  <expan>unsich<ex>er</ex></expan> sein
                                                  <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., das
                                                  <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                                                  <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir darczu niht wol
                                                  <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>, als irselbs
                                                wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt, uns
                                                  <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> denn die
                                                  <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> lewt, die die sache
                                                berürt, mit <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> benennet.
                                                Denn wo wir ewch lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                                dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Leonhardi.</ab>
</div>
